title: Ozzy Osbourne - The Early Years 1981-1982 (The j-m-gart Edition)
description:
Hello Metalheads!
Here comes the first DVD from my new Early Years Collection!
This is Ozzy 81-82 Era,and it is 4 Concerts!
1: Palladium Theater, NY - 05.02.81 (Audience)
2: After Hours Performance, NY - 28.04.81 (Pro)
3: Rosemont Horizon, Chicago, IL - 24.01.82 (Audience)
4: Irvine, Ca - 12.06.82 (Pro)

I have Enhanced Audio and Video!
The audio are in 2.0 and 5.1 Sound!

I think this is a nice DVD from the early Ozzy,and i hope all like it!
Please seed this for a long time!

Meny and Chapters!
